::Hot Rod::

"Well actually I brought your parts back, and put them in the CR. You
seemed beyond repair," he started.
"I went to my room, and morned. When I finally came out, I went to get
orders from Zardus. Thats when I walked in, and saw you. I dont what
they did, but I'm glad they did."
He kissed her. There wasn't much passion behind it, but it was on the
lips. He wasn't sure how she would react if he *really* kissed her.
